File structure info:

1. src/ - Contains all the python source code
2. docs/ - Contains HTML documentation for the python code
3. data/ - Contains dataset obtained using src/dataset_fetcher.py

Requirements:

1. python3
2. pip3
3. Various python packages required are listed in requirements.txt 

Usage:

1. Ensure the working directory is the top-level directory of this project
2. Install the required packages using "pip3 install -r requirements.txt"
3. Change working directory to "src" and then use "python3 hits.py" 